===Noun===
'''[[semi-]][[trailer]]'''
# A [[trailer]] without a [[front]] [[axle]] and with [[wheel]]s only at the [[trailing]] end, designed to be pulled via a [[pivot]]ing arrangement which also partially supports its weight.
